{"tid":322453,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[KPOP] Mnet《PRODUCE 101 Season 2》討論區(147)","createTime":"2017-07-14T22:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T22:26:05.000Z","uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faf682937e3760f499632e984aa6568f1d4534e4","tid":322453,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T22:20:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>歡迎加入101 S2討論區</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n節目簡介及精華片段&mdash;#1<br />\nWanna One成員介紹&mdash;#2<br />\n節目中字&mdash;#3<br />\nFAQ&mdash;#4<br />\n舊post及開post template&mdash;#5<br />\n</span></span></div><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Fc7g6CO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFc7g6CO.jpg&h=f2770b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eF9bZXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeF9bZXT.jpg&h=b1dac4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/govRZrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgovRZrH.jpg&h=32090ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/k1ylQQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fk1ylQQA.jpg&h=bfcb05ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n《PRODUCE 101第二季》是Mnet於2017年推出的韓國首個「經紀公司大型企劃男團」新男團選拔／生存實境節目，以101名來自不同經紀公司的男練習生為主角。在節目中，男練習生需要共同生活，接受訓練，以及完成各種不同的任務。國民製作人（觀眾）最終通過投票方式選出11名男練習生，而該11名練習生將會組成限定男團進行活動。第二季國民製作人代表由BoA擔任。<br />\n <br />\n節目於四月七日首播，六月十六日完成放送。節目最終以11人組成Wanna One出道，組合成員包括姜丹尼爾、朴志訓、李大輝、金在煥、邕聖祐、朴佑鎮、賴冠霖、尹智聖、黃旼泫、裴珍映及河成雲。Wanna One將由YMC Entertainment管理，合約暫定於2018年12月期滿。<br />\n <br />\nPRODUCE 101 第二季First Stage 나야나 (PICK ME):<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNIld_iEc67s&d=zNW%2FefYGC5uhRXi%2FbKZfvSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=89c88e6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NIld_iEc67s</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n導師(Trainee Team)：<br />\n<a href=\"http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/training\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmnettv.interest.me%2Fproduce101%2Fsub%2Ftraining&d=zNW%2FefYGC5uhRXi%2FbKZfvSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0f4e75b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/training</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TMEtEtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTMEtEtM.png&h=abc095f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n練習生profile：<br />\n<a href=\"http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/profile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmnettv.interest.me%2Fproduce101%2Fsub%2Fprofile&d=zNW%2FefYGC5uhRXi%2FbKZfvSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c9aec2ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://mnettv.interest.me/produce101/sub/profile</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yAqJjqK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyAqJjqK.jpg&h=69e45565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZBrzMbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZBrzMbE.jpg&h=1799896b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GG9PJb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGG9PJb4.jpg&h=7c1a3895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/h1YG56W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh1YG56W.jpg&h=24fc8395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2n9nL2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2n9nL2e.jpg&h=bae106d3&s=